ColtExpress Score ThreeTuples 2021

The results in the tabs below show the MCTS parameters optimised for ColtExpress when using a ScoreHeuristic instead of the default one. The change is that NTBEA uses 3-Tuples as well as 2- and 1-Tuples. The opponents (OSLA and MCTS; not RND) also use the ScoreHeuristic, so should improve in quality as well.

The aim of this experiment was to see if 3-Tuple data changed the results in any interesting way.
